<div class="content" name="NETLOGON_DELTA_ENUM_ARRAY" uuid="82d47318-c4d8-4583-86a6-ce186504bcba"><p>The <b>NETLOGON_DELTA_ENUM_ARRAY</b> structure defines an
array of <span><a href="b5e7d25a-40b2-41c8-9611-98f53358af66#gt_bac72edb-4ce9-4baa-8977-f33e331b2b5e" data-linktype="relative-path">delta</a></span> objects.</p><dl>
<dd>
<div><pre> typedef struct _NETLOGON_DELTA_ENUM_ARRAY {
   DWORD CountReturned;
   [size_is(CountReturned)] PNETLOGON_DELTA_ENUM Deltas;
 } NETLOGON_DELTA_ENUM_ARRAY,
  *PNETLOGON_DELTA_ENUM_ARRAY;
</pre></div>
</dd></dl><p><b>CountReturned:</b> The number of elements in the
Deltas field.</p><p><b>Deltas:</b> An array of <b>NETLOGON_DELTA_ENUM</b>
structures, as specified in section <span><a href="20e5863c-0142-40f6-a914-f352a9d66047" data-linktype="relative-path">2.2.1.5.11</a></span>.</p></div>